# Paths agents should skip when assembling default context.
# Override case-by-case when the user asks explicitly (e.g. "include archived").

# Reference content — read intentionally, not by default
**/_examples/

# Archived notes — kept for history, not for synthesis
notes/archive/
notes/**/*.archived.md

# Build outputs (if any prototype graduates to a sub-project)
**/node_modules/
**/dist/
**/build/

# OS / editor noise
.DS_Store
.vscode/
.idea/
